This function returns system time in yyyy-MM-dd format.  Syntax  STRING  time:currentDate()  Examples  EXAMPLE 1  define stream inputStream (symbol string, price long, volume long);
from inputStream select symbol , time:currentDate() as currentTime 
insert into outputStream;  This query returns symbol from inputStream andcurrent date of the system in yyyy-MM-dd format as current time to the outputStream

